uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.rest.service

Class SimpleOperationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.rest.service.SimpleOperationService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOperationService

    public class SimpleOperationService
extends Object
implements IOperationService
    An implementation of IOperationService. By default it will use a singleton Graph generated using the GraphFactory. All operations are simple delegated to the graph. Pre and post operation hooks are available by extending this class and implementing preOperationHook and/or postOperationHook.

    By default queries will be executed with an UNKNOWN user containing no auths. The createUser() method should be overridden and a User object should be created from the http request.
